txt.en: Complete Quests of the Cape of Umbar
You explored all of the Cape of Umbar.

Once beneath the rule of the ruthless Heirs of Castamir, the Cape of Umbar emerges from a shadowy chrysalis as a land reborn. The citizens struggle with newfound freedom, the sins of the past, and a desire to cling to the rites and customs of their culture, as they are guided by the hands of Kindred of the Coins.
You defeated a great many enemies in the Cape of Umbar.
